com.google.api.ads.adwords.axis.utility.extension.delegates

Class AbstractGetDelegate<T,S>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.ads.adwords.axis.utility.extension.delegates.AbstractBaseDelegate<S>
      • com.google.api.ads.adwords.axis.utility.extension.delegates.AbstractGetDelegate<T,S>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of object that the Service works with, for example Campaign, AdGroup, etc.
    S - the service interface class. This is a class representing a SOAP service.

    Implementation is not thread-safe, because AdWordsSession and Apache Axis service objects are not thread-safe.

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractGetMutateDelegate, DataAdGroupBidLandscapeDelegate, DataCriterionBidLandscapeDelegate, LocationCriterionDelegate, MediaDelegate

    public abstract class AbstractGetDelegate<T,S>
extends AbstractBaseDelegate<S>
    Abstract class that encapsulates gets, fields and selectors.
    Author:
    Julian Toledo
